}}],"oddsUpdateTime":"2026-04-12T00:18:02.000Z","raceComments":"{\"comment\":\"1. MORINDOO turned in a fine effort to score by 3.5 lengths at today's course and distance when resuming from a layoff last start. Needs to be at her best to beat this field but she can win again. 8. EPICURIAN LAD is a 18-start maiden who returned last time and finished fifth at this track over 1600m, beaten 3 lengths. Will take a lot from that hit-out and looks a strong chance to break through. 5. IRELAND ALEXANDER was comfortably accounted for when third last time out over 1700m at Dortmund, beaten 3 lengths. That followed a win at Dortmund at the previous outing. It doesn't get any easier but on her best form she is capable of a big performance. 4. BERRYGATE ran below expectations last start, finishing seventh and beaten 13 lengths at this track over 1600m. Suitably placed so anticipating a better run this time.\",\"runners\":[1,8,5,4],\"exclusive\":false}","tips":{"tipType":"Standard","tipster":"Wett Star Germany","tipRunnerNumbers":[1,2,5,8]},"ratings":[{"ratingType":"Rating","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,8,4,5]},{"ratingType":"Last12Months","ratingRunnerNumbers":[8,7,10,5]},{"ratingType":"Recent","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,5,3,2]},{"ratingType":"Distance","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,5,2,3]},{"ratingType":"Class","ratingRunnerNumbers":[4,5,2,10]},{"ratingType":"Time","ratingRunnerNumbers":[5,1,6,4]},{"ratingType":"Overall","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,5,4,8]}],"multiLegApproximates":[],"betTypes":[{"wageringProduct":"Win","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":3,"venueMnemonic":"DDF","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Place","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":3,"venueMnemonic":"DDF","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Quinella","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":3,"venueMnemonic":"DDF","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Exacta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":3,"venueMnemonic":"DDF","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Trifecta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":3,"venueMnemonic":"DDF","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Quaddie","firstLeg"